  "title": "Service Crew (PART TIME)",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Hiring – Part-Time Customer Service & Heritage Representative</strong><br /><br />📍 <em>The Peranakan Club | Orchard Road</em></p><p>The Peranakan Club is a living heritage space where culture is shared through food, stories, and human connection. We are looking for friendly, caring individuals to join us as <strong>Part-Time Customer Service & Heritage Representatives</strong>.</p><p>If you enjoy meeting people, sharing culture, and creating meaningful guest experiences, we’d love to hear from you.</p><h3>Your Role</h3><p>• Welcome and assist guests warmly<br />• Share simple stories about Peranakan culture, food, and traditions<br />• Support basic service duties (seating, orders, payments)<br />• Assist with gallery tours, workshops, or events (training provided)<br />• Maintain a clean, calm, and welcoming environment</p><h3>We’re Looking For</h3><p>• Friendly, patient, and service-oriented<br />• Comfortable speaking to guests (English required; Mandarin/Malay a bonus)<br />• Interest in heritage, food, or community work<br />• Able to work weekends or selected weekdays<br />• Seniors, caregivers returning to work, and career switchers welcome</p><h3>What We Offer</h3><p>• Flexible part-time hours<br />• On-job training in customer service & heritage storytelling<br />• Supportive, care-first workplace<br />• Meaningful work that connects culture with community<br />• Opportunity to grow into full-time roles</p><p><strong>To apply:</strong><br />WhatsApp your name, availability, and short intro to: 9889 5573<br />or email: hellosayang@theperanakanclub.com</p><p><em>Come be part of a team that serves with heart — where every guest experience carries culture forward.</em></p><p></p>",
